resources.name: Install AppleWWDRCA.cer
resources.conditional: not_if "security find-certificate -Z /Library/Keychains/System.keychain -a -c 'Apple Worldwide Developer Relations Certification Authority'"

resources.name: install_java_from_dmg
resources.id:
hdiutil attach jdk-7u71-macosx-x64.dmg
installer -pkg "/Volumes/JDK 7 Update 71"/*.pkg -target /
hdiutil detach "/Volumes/JDK 7 Update 71"
